OL,3,CFrench mayor's plea after village's
OL,4,Cmissing road sign ends up in Somerset
OL,6,FThe mayor of a French village whose
OL,7,Fmissing road sign appeared in Somerset
OL,8,Flast week has politely asked the
OL,9,FEnglish to just take a picture of it
OL,10,Fnext time.
OL,12,FPranksters have replaced a "Welcome to
OL,13,FMidsomer Norton" sign with a road sign
OL,14,Ffrom the village of Sallespisse in
OL,15,Fsouth west France.
OL,17,FLast year, Midsomer Norton's road sign
OL,18,Fwas swapped with one from Frome but
OL,19,Fnow the Somerset sign-swapper appears
OL,20,Fto have gone international.
OL,26,@tD@\OUuD@PO]
