OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776888354
OL,3,CFrench mayor's plea after village's
OL,4,Cmissing road sign ends up in Somerset
OL,6,FSallespisse, which is considered an
OL,7,Famusing place name to French-speakers,
OL,8,Fis no stranger to having its sign
OL,9,Fstolen either. But when it vanished
OL,10,Fsix months ago nobody expected it
OL,11,Fwould end up 540 miles away in
OL,12,FSomerset.
OL,14,FMonsieur Francis Grinet, the Mayor of
OL,15,FSallespisse, said: "While seeing our
OL,16,Fsign in an English town might seem
OL,17,Famusing, it nonetheless constitutes
OL,18,Fdamage to our local council. We have
OL,19,Fto replace them every time and each
OL,20,Freplacement comes at a cost."
OL,26,@wD@TOU|D@]O]
