OL,3,CFrench mayor's plea after village's
OL,4,Cmissing road sign ends up in Somerset
OL,6,FSallespisse is a pretty rural village
OL,7,Fin the south west of France with a
OL,8,Fpopulation of just 600 people.
OL,10,FMonsieur Grinet said: "Located less
OL,11,Fthan 100 km from the Atlantic Ocean
OL,12,Fand the Pyrenees, this is a place many
OL,13,Ftourists pass through during their
OL,14,Fholidays. It was probably during one
OL,15,Fof these trips that an English
OL,16,Fnational took the sign indicating the
OL,17,Fentrance to our village.
OL,19,F"He did not leave us a sign from his
OL,20,FBritish village in exchange."
OL,26,@rD@WOU{D@AOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
