PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776888354
OL,3,CFrench mayor's plea after village's
OL,4,Cmissing road sign ends up in Somerset
OL,6,FMr Grinet said: "I'm glad to know that
OL,7,Four English friends were able to learn
OL,8,Fabout our town thanks to this prank. I
OL,9,Fencourage them to take a picture in
OL,10,Ffront of the sign the next time they
OL,11,Fdrive through our village, but please
OL,12,Fleave it in place!"
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@SO]
